title: [Royal Koyanagi] St. Penalty Gakuen Goku (cover and omake) [Toni
description:
This is just the cover, the omake, and post script pages that I was commissioned to translate by 2Hip, of WWOEC.

The manga was translated by various translators from the monthly periodicals, and some people made their own compilations from that.  Someone may have posted such a compilation here.  Otherwise, please check with 2Hip at WWOEC.

More info at my blog on Wordpress.
